            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 3200,
            "LocalizeKR": "신기한 일이죠.",
            "LocalizeJP": "不思議ですよね。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_01_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20054,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2005401,
            "DisplayOrder": 610,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 12470,
            "LocalizeKR": "밀레니엄에서 그랬던 것처럼,\n여기에서도 밤하늘을 올려다볼\n수 있는데도.",
            "LocalizeJP": "ミレニアムと変わらず、\nここでも夜空を見上げることは\nできるのに。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20054,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2005401,
            "DisplayOrder": 620,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7500,
            "LocalizeKR": "이곳에서 빛나는 별은,\n우리가 아는 것과는\n어딘가 다르네요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "瞬く星は、\n私たちの知るものとは\n異なっていて。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20054,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2005401,
            "DisplayOrder": 630,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 13100,
            "LocalizeKR": "좀처럼\n말로 표현하기 어려운……\n신비한 감각이라고나 할까요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "どうにも言語化が難しい……\n形容しがたい感覚です。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20054,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2005401,
            "DisplayOrder": 640,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 3500,
            "LocalizeKR": "네……?!",
            "LocalizeJP": "はい……！？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20054,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2005401,
            "DisplayOrder": 650,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 16330,
            "LocalizeKR": "가, 감사합니다.\n치, 칭찬해 주신 것으로\n이해하겠어요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "あ、ありがとうございます。\nその……褒め言葉として\n受け取っておきます。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20054,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2005401,
            "DisplayOrder": 660,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 4500,
            "LocalizeKR": "……같은 밤하늘 아래에\n있다고 하더라도.",
            "LocalizeJP": "……同じ夜空の下にいても。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_04_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20054,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2005401,
            "DisplayOrder": 670,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 10000,
            "LocalizeKR": "모두가 모두를\n이해할 수 있는 것은 아니겠죠.",
            "LocalizeJP": "互いが互いを理解できるとは\n限りません。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20054,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2005401,
            "DisplayOrder": 680,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8000,
            "LocalizeKR": "하지만 적어도\n같은 하늘 아래에 있다는 것은\n확실하니.",
            "LocalizeJP": "ですが少なくとも、\n「同じ」\n夜空の下にいるのですから。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_05_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20054,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2005401,
            "DisplayOrder": 690,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 12830,
            "LocalizeKR": "서로를 이해할 계기 정도는,\n되지 않을까요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "互いを理解する\nきっかけくらいには、\nなるのではないでしょうか。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20054,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2005401,
            "DisplayOrder": 700,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 6,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7500,
            "LocalizeKR": "저는 그렇게 생각해요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "私は、そんな風に思うのです。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle6",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_06_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20054,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2005401,
            "DisplayOrder": 710,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 6,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 13000,
            "LocalizeKR": "선생님은, 어떻게 생각하시나요?",
            "LocalizeJP": "先生は、どう思われますか？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
